Class SetupControlMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.umass.cs.msocket.SetupControlMessage

  • public class SetupControlMessage
extends Object
    This class implements the setup control message format, serialization and de-serialization. Setup control messages are sent in the beginning to establish the connection.

    1.0
